description: 60 ft high, 12,000 square feet of indoor climbing gym area. Colorful and friendly! The Rock Oasis is a great place to climb in Toronto! FEATURES • 15,000 square feet of climbing surface • Colourful walls with seamless smearable texture • Walls with a wide variety of angles • Technical outdoor style route setting • Lots of bouldering • Fun people work and climb here TOP ROPE CLIMBING The first time you visit The Rock Oasis you must fill in our climbing registration and liability waiver. If you do not know how to tie in and belay, please see the New Climber page. For experienced climbers who know how to tie in and belay, you will be asked to pass a top rope belay certification. We will confirm that you know how to tie into the rope and that you are a safe belayer. This process is for everyone's safety and therefore there is no charge for this service. LEAD CLIMBING If you want to lead climb at The Rock Oasis then you must take our lead climbing course or be an experienced lead climber. Experienced lead climbers must make an appointment to take a lead test. A $25 fee will apply as follows: either 1) refunded if climber is a safe lead climber and lead belayer or 2) 1/2 hour refresher if climber demonstrates 95% of required skills or 3) partial payment towards lead climbing course. Whether you are a first time climber, or a seasoned veteran you will find a variety of options to challenge yourself. Our fitness area is available for all levels of athletes (novice to crossfitters) and includes a treadmill, rower, stationary bike, assisted and free weights as well as exercise balls. The campus board and system wall is located in the same area, an additional training tool for climbers wishing to advance to that next level. Aside from the climbing walls and fitness area, free wi-fi, a comfortable lounge area, a pool table and a selection of drinks and snacks provide a social hub for the local climbing community.

Klimcentrum Neoliet Eindhoven-Zuid is per 15 september 2012 open en gevestigd op de Genneper Parken in het gebouw van de Fontys Sport Hogeschool. Er zijn hier uitstekende voorklimwanden, een rotswand, klettersteigs en touwparcouren. Het centrum is bij uitstek geschikt voor het opleiden van klimmers en kader. De gehele ruimte is hiervoor af te huren. Maar juist ook voor een avontuurlijke belevenis zoals onze feestjes en arrangementen. name: High Altitude Climbing
description: High Altitude Climbing centre is Pietermaritzburg's only indoor rock-climbing gym. We offer once-off climbing sessions, memberships, courses and lessons as well as group functions and birthday parties. We also organise school clubs and are involved in the regional and national school climbing competitions. Our 12 metre high indoor wall is the perfect place to start climbing and caters to all levels of climbing, young and old! It is a fantastic family activity! We also run regular out-door climbing days where you can get the feel for the real thing. We have all the gear you need, so there is no need to buy any equipment before you start, and when you are ready to invest in your own gear, our well stocked shop will have what you need. We are located on Mayors Walk in Pietermaritzburg, at the Pmb Sports Development Centre. Other sports that are offered include gymnastics, judo, karate and MMA.

name: Muro de Escalada Municipal de Brusque
description: Foi inaugurado em 6 de julho de 2012 o primeiro Muro de Escalada público de Santa Catarina, no Parque Zoobotânico da cidade de Brusque. O projeto idealizado pelo coordenador de Aventura do Parque Zoobotânico Álvaro Walendowsky, conta com uma estrutura de 10 metros de altura com 3 faces para escalar com diferentes inclinações e uma via exclusiva para o rapel. A montagem da estrutura foi uma parceria entre a Salamandra Escola de Montanha, Garra Aventura e Núcleo Ecológico Mutuca. O resultado foi bem gratificante, principalmente pelo fato de ser um Muro público e também por ajudar a desenvolver um novo pólo de escalada no estado. A estrutura esportiva incrementa as atrações oferecidas à comunidade no Parque Zoobotânico. Na entrega oficial do Muro de Escalada, o Prefeito de Brusque, Paulo Eccel, destacou a importância do Parque Zoobotânico para o turismo em Brusque. “Além do cuidado com os animais e as plantas, esse espaço agora também tem estrutura para a prática esportiva de aventura, que é uma das áreas que cresce muito no Brasil e incrementa o turismo”, ressaltou o prefeito.

Inside a world of adventure possibilities awaits- with the worlds tallest indoor climbing routes, a map/book room, lounge area, classroom, and strength and conditioning equipment, we have everything you need to make your next adventure happen. If you are serious about outdoor adventure (or you want to be) this is the place for you. We are not a climbing gym in the traditional sense- we consider our facility a place to train for outdoor adventure sports and activities. For this reason everything we do is just like we would do in the outdoors. Well teach you the same techniques we use outside. And if youve never climbed outside before, this is a great place to make the transition! We offer way more than climbing, too. With our amazing trips, classes, and sense of community, if you are interested in outdoor adventure you are sure to find a place here!

name: Equilibrio Vertical
description: Escalada é uma técnica cujo fim é atingir o cume de uma parede rochosa, de um bloco ou de um muro de escalada. O terreno vai de alguns metros para o bloco ou o muro de escalada, podendo chegar a centenas de metros para as paredes rochosas. Boulder é uma das modalidades da escalada que consiste em escalar pequenos blocos, geralmente com altura não superior a 5 metros, onde os movimentos são geralmente de maior dificuldade técnica e exigem força. Para a prática de boulder não é necessário o uso dos equipamentos de segurança como cordas e mosquetões. Os equipamentos utilizados são'colon' sapatilhas, carbonato de magnésio (para as mãos) e o Crash Pad (colchão de queda). Também é necessário um segurança de corpo, cujo papel é fazer com que o escalador caia em pé sobre o crash pad. O muro da Equilíbrio Vertical é um complexo de boulder e foi desenvolvido com uma variedade de inclinações para simular a escalada na rocha, que não é apenas o suficiente para o treino como também o mais indicado por escaladores do mundo inteiro. Aqui você vai melhorar o seu desempenho e garantir a sua diversão!

name: Wolf Mountain
description: Wolf Mountain Indoor Climbing Centre first opened its doors to the public in October 2005 and was based in a small industrial unit in Racecourse Road, Wolverhampton, West Midlands. The Centre was hugely popular and attracted a variety of people. However, the demand for indoor climbing was significantly higher than we had anticipated and therefore prompted the search for larger premises. In December 2009, after months of planning and construction, we relocated and currently operate from what was formerly a local authority swimming pool that now houses some extremely impressive climbing walls. Set in a beautiful location, the Centre boasts excellent facilities and offers a range of adventurous activities. The Centre has top rope, bouldering, abseiling and lead climbing walls. In addition to this, there is an indoor caving system, archery gallery, conference room for hire, designated climbing area for kid's parties and two themed party rooms. Wolf Mountain caters for individuals and groups of all abilities and prides itself on the excellent facilities and committed staff team. For the less energetic visitor or spectator, there is a cafe and several sit down viewing areas. Situated near to the City Centre, Wolf Mountain is easily accessible by public transport and for those choosing to drive, there is ample free car parking provision.
